{"tid":1782913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃店飲食做野]飲食界功能組別申請","createTime":"2019-12-14T11:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T11:28:22.000Z","uid":283442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dfdaa48c3ab8162b5842e4d80900c6e1391cd451","tid":1782913,"uid":283442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈宜家要做野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個手足食完黃店唔該 <strong>唔該</strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>叫老細登記做飲食界功能組別 俾埋份form 佢填</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n如果老闆已經係區選投過票就用REO-43<br />\n乜都無登記過就用REO-41</span><br />\n<br />\n補link:<br />\n介紹: <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/cat_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fcat_c.pdf&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=ef9d093d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/cat_c.pdf</a><br />\nREO-43:<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-43%28C%29.pdf&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=1600a175\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C).pdf</a><br />\nREO-41: <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C%29.pdf&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=2d2a86db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C).pdf</a><br />\n黃店飲食功能組別你我有責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0000ac962568aec2b6f3bfbd5d49034ccf9bb8b2","tid":178291